                  <desc type="foundation">During time of King Fasilädäs (r. 1632-67). Ras ʿƎšät, according to the written "History" of the Church, during time of King Fasilädäs (r. 1632-67).</desc>
                  <ab type="history">Däbr. Two churches are in the compound: one very recent, one somewhat older. The medieval church of Säwnä is at a different place in the vicinity. The church stands at the administrative border between Tǝgray and ʿAfar regions.
</ab>
